^-{        Quick Tricks         }
^-|HT|f|CP||FP||at|^B@2^Z@3What is Quick Tricks?|
PG| ***** 120 ***** |


AT|
Quick Tricks (QT) is the number of tricks you expect to win in a suit on the first two rounds of that suit. Only 2 Quick Trick per suit. Note: Jacks are never "quick."|
PG| ***** 121 ***** |


AT|

How is it done?|
PG| ***** 122 ***** |


AT|
Simple. Any Ace gets one, any Ace-King gets two, an Ace-Queen is one and one half, for an King-Queen count one, and one half quick trick for any King-x. So, A=1, AK=2, KQ=1, AQ=1 1/2, and Kx=1/2.|
PG| ***** 123 ***** |


AT|

Let us look at a few examples.|
